data.description: Welcome to your new home in the Lincoln Park Subdivision in Titusville, FL! This 3 bedroom 2 bathroom brick home has an open floor plan, enclosed front porch, and cozy fireplace. The electric panel has been newly updated, and the garage and backyard areas have more than enough room for you and your guests. The property comes with a shed for additional storage, a horseshoe zone, and outdoor seating area located on the side of the home. The living room and dining room areas are large and spacious. The floors are tile and carpeted through out the home, and wood covered panels on the walls give the home a nice warm feel. The oversized garage has room for all types of vehicles and can also be used for additional storage. Call and schedule your appointment today!
